OOC: Okay guys, from now on Speedbreaker is Breakdown, (thanks KSLAWDOGG


Sinnertwin finally parted through some clouds, his arms totally
outstreched, he looked down and could see three Decepticons, as he flew
towards them.

Motormaster turned towards Cyclonus. "Well, aparently we need Stratus
and Astrotrain. Plus if my Stunticons didnt get lost." he said
aggressivly, as he looked up to the sky. Behind him Sinnertwin landed,
and Transformed into his creature mode. He began to sniff the area, and
was moving towards a group of trees.
______________________________________________________________________

Further off in the distance, two figueres parted between some clouds.
"Are we even going in the right direction?" Breakdown asked worridly. 

"Sure we are." Wildrider said, more ignoring his fellow Stunticon. They
flew gracefully close to the ocean, water splashing apon their metalic
forms. Breakdown looked around him.

"Are Drag-Strip and Dead End still behind us?" he asked. 

Wildrider didnt even bother to look. "Sure they are." as they rounded
another large rock.
